3 SECTION 2. APPROPRIATION - SUPERINTENDENT OF PUBLIC INSTRUCTION -
4 SECURE STORAGE OF A STUDENT'S PERSONAL ELECTRONIC DEVICE. There is
5 appropriated out of any moneys in the general fund in the state treasury, not otherwise
6 appropriated, the sum of $1,890,000, or so much of the sum as may be necessary, to the
7 superintendent of public instruction for the purpose of providing schools with secure containers
8 for the storage of students' personal electronic devices during the schoolday, for the biennium
9 beginning July 1, 2025, and ending June 30, 2027.
